            </div>
            <div type="edition" subtype="transcription" ana="b1">
                <p xml:lang="heb">ב<num value="9"><g type="nine-vertical-strokes"/></num> לתמוז שנת
                        <num value="18"><g type="sixteen-plus-two-vertical-strokes"
                        /></num><lb/><unclear>הנע</unclear>ל קוסמל<supplied reason="lost"
                        >ך</supplied>
                    <unclear>בר קינא</unclear><supplied reason="lost"
                        >ל</supplied><lb/><unclear>מס</unclear>כנה ל<unclear>מנ</unclear>קדה
                        <unclear>ח</unclear>ס <num value="4"><g
                            type="three-plus-one-vertical-strokes"/></num></p>
            </div>
            <div type="translation" ana="b1">
                <p>On the 9th of Tammuz, year 16+2 (=18)<lb/>Qosmal[ak] son of Qayni[l] brought
                    in<lb/>(to the) storehouse of Makkedah: w(heat), s(eahs), 3+1 (=4)</p>
            </div>
            <div type="commentary" ana="b1">
                <p>Both the last two strokes of the date in line 1 and the last stroke of the
                    quantity in line 3 are written supralinearly. Only one other inscription shows
                    Qosmalak with a patronym (A11.9, Idum 0425).</p>
            </div>
            <!-- The bibl has more contained elements. What is the possible list of values of the biblScope/@type? 
             -->
